data.description: **Seller will entertain or counter offers between range pricing $390,000-405,000.** Come see this year-old Mattamy Acacia floor plan home located in the highly sought after Saguaro Trails Community and it's amenities! It offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a flex room. Enjoy the spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and black granite countertops while entertaining your guests. The rear yard is just waiting for your personal touch. It comes with refrigerator, washer and dryer! This is a perfect starter home or for those looking to downsize. Schedule your tour today!
